 plus\r\n\r\nWhat we offer:\r\n\r\nCompetitive compensation package Ground floor opportunity within rapidly growing tech startup Great collaborative team environment Full Benefits Fun perks\r\n\r\nLocation - NYC, Flatiron District\r\n\r\nWe welcome your cover letter with a description of your previous complete experience and your resume. Applicants must be authorized to work in the US as we are unable to sponsor. Kasisto is an equal opportunity employer.','Software engineer (back end)','','publish','closed','closed','','software-engineer-back-end','','','2022-07-07 21:21:52','2022-07-07 21:21:52','',0,'http://localhost/?post_type=jobs&#038;p=10',0,'jobs','',0),(11,1,'2022-07-07 19:49:27','2022-07-07 19:49:27','a:7:{s:8:\"location\";a:1:{i:0;a:1:{i:0;a:3:{s:5:\"param\";s:9:\"post_type\";s:8:\"operator\";s:2:\"==\";s:5:\"value\";s:4:\"jobs\";}}}s:8:\"position\";s:6:\"normal\";s:5:\"style\";s:7:\"default\";s:15:\"label_placement\";s:3:\"top\";s:21:\"instruction_placement\";s:5:\"label\";s:14:\"hide_on_screen\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";}','Jobs','jobs','publish','closed','closed','','group_62c738b6118cc','','','2022-07-07 19:49:27','2022-07-07 19:49:27','',0,'http://localhost/?post_type=acf-field-group&#038;p=11',0,'acf-field-group','',0),(12,1,'2022-07-07 19:49:27','2022-07-07 19:49:27','a:10:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"text\";s:12:\"instructions\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"required\";i:0;s:17:\"conditional_logic\";i:0;s:7:\"wrapper\";a:3:{s:5:\"width\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"class\";s:0:\"\";s:2:\"id\";s:0:\"\";}s:13:\"default_value\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"placeholder\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"prepend\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"append\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"maxlength\";s:0:\"\";}','Company name','company_name','publish','closed','closed','','field_62c738b90ada2','','','2022-07-07 19:49:27','2022-07-07 19:49:27','',11,'http://localhost/?post_type=acf-field&p=12',0,'acf-field','',0),(13,1,'2022-07-07 19:56:03','2022-07-07 19:56:03','','logo2','','inherit','open','closed','','logo2','','','2022-07-07 19:56:03','20